fr.zcraft.quartzlib.tools.items

Class CraftingRecipes

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.zcraft.quartzlib.core.QuartzComponent
      • fr.zcraft.quartzlib.tools.items.CraftingRecipes

  • public class CraftingRecipes
extends QuartzComponent
    This class provides various utilities for Crafting Recipes management. Crafting recipes can be registered safely before the plugin/server is loaded. If this is the case, their registration will be done at plugin initialization.

        Returns:
